title: Arturia APR2600v, CS-80v, Moog Modular, Minimoog with presets
description:
This is the Arturia APR2600v, CS-80v, Moog Modular, and the Minimoog. Also included are great presets for each unit.
These are stand alone and/or work in Logic, Protools, etc.

For Mac OS X - I use a PPC os 10.4.11, not sure how they work on Intel.
Leopard Protools updates included.

Versions are:

ARP2600v - 1.0 (update link below)
CS-80v - 1.6
Moog Modular - 2.2
Minimoog - 1.6

Have fun.
